leaf nodes (encapsulating explicit cost and duration matrices extended by decorator wrappers). Developed the recursive ActivityPlan class as the central composite node , managing 
internal arrays via component manipulation vectors (addComponent() / removeComponent()) and implementing recursive mathematical algorithms to automatically aggregate deep total costs 
and total durations across complex, nested trip itineraries. 
•	Behavioral Command Pattern Framework: Co-architected and laid the foundational behavioral logic infrastructure for user interaction tracking within the com.smarttravel.command 
domain. Structured the behavioral execution interface Command mapping uniform execute() and undo() protocols. Developed the skeleton of concrete operational commands including 
AddActivityCommand, RemoveActivityCommand, and ClearPlanCommand , configuring them to ingest explicit contextual parameters regarding active composite nodes (ActivityPlan) and 
target components (Activity) to safely mutate or revert model states without direct GUI coupling. 
•	Graphical User Interface Design & Panel Integration: Served as the primary visual interface designer for the desktop environment (com.smarttravel.gui). Built the structured 
framework for the application's visual tree, establishing the main layout managers and visual sub-panels. Programmed the primary layout integration boundaries for the custom data 
visualization components (ChartPanel), configuring them to cleanly handle live telemetry redraws upon receiving data-fresh observer notifications from the concurrent weather providers. 
•	Inter-Module Behavioral Coupling: Programmed the necessary event-dispatching listeners to map visual GUI user controls directly to backend design pattern logic flows. Wired the 
